        <div class="sticky sticky--p sticky-r1n">
          <span class="sticky-title">What's next 🔭</span>
          <p>Expanding beyond microfiber towels into additional detailing tools and chemical products. The mission stays the same: honest gear for real enthusiasts.</p>
