      <div class="os-mission-right">
        <div class="sticky sticky--b sticky-r2" style="max-width:340px;">
          <span class="sticky-title">Our promise ✌️</span>
          <div class="sticky-quote">"We refuse to compromise on quality, but we also refuse to price people out of the hobby."</div>
